mbering Hadith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Darimi reported: Abu Huraira, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cI have divided the night into three parts. I sleep in a third of it, I stand in prayer for a third of it, and for a third of it I recall the traditions of the Messenger of Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25891,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/04\/imam-most-knowledge-quran-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":42238,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Imams: Most knowledgeable  of Quran should lead prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best versed in the recitation of the Quran should lead the prayer. If they are equal in their recitation, then the one most knowledgeable of them in the Sunnah. If are equal in knowledge of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28579,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/01\/ummah-ilm-fiqh-hadith\/","url_meta":{"origin":42238,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Allah guides people of Fiqh, Hadith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah will not let my nation agree upon misguidance. The hand of Allah is over the united community.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"The interpretation of the united community, according to the scholars, are the people of Fiqh,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19573,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/25\/ahmad-sunnah-act-fiqh-hadith\/","url_meta":{"origin":42238,"position":4},"title":"Ahmad on Sunnah: Not act on hadith until authenticated, understood","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 25, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: Abdullah ibn Ahmad said, \u201cI asked my father Ahmad ibn Hanbal about a man who has books, within which are the sayings of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and the companions and the followers, but he cannot distinguish weak and rejected narrations,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":642,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/21\/trust-heaven-quran-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":42238,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Faith: The trust descended from heaven to people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 21, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"The covenant of faithfulness descended from the heavens and settled in the hearts of men. The Quran was revealed and they read it in the Quran and learned it from the